nodes.text: Qualung Tulla was a male Aqualish who worked for Meeko Ghintee during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. In 32 BBY, he wanted by the Toydarian Rozatta for stealing her fuel cell shipments. His bounty, worth 3,000 credits alive and 1,500 dead, was claimed by the Mandalorian-turned Bounty hunter Jango Fett.
